<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>체스 게임 대기방</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./src/index.css">
</head>
<body>

<h1>♟️ 체스 게임 대기방♟</h1>

<div id="game-entry">

  <form enctype="text/plain" action="/game/start" method="get">
    <label for="game-entry">방 번호를 입력하여 시작하기</label>
    <br>
    <input type="text" name="gameId" value="1234">
    <button type="submit">입장하기</button>
  </form>

  <form action="/game/start" method="post">
    <label for="game-entry">방 이름과 비밀번호를 입력하여 시작하기 (없을 시 새로 방 생성)</label>
    <br>
    <input type="text" name="title" value="1234">
    <input type="text" name="password" value="1234">
    <button type="submit">입장하기</button>
  </form>

</div>

</body>
</html>
